reviewText: I will let the fact that this DVD won the 2013 Aurora Award for high standard of excellence in the film industry speak for me. You might not be familiar with this award but you are probably familiar with some of the past winners: Canon, Coca-Cola, Geico, Sesame Workshop, The History Channel, Disney, CBS, MSNBC, Time Warner Cable, and many others. This is a great video that is sure to teach viewers of all ages something new about water.
